title: OUR BABY BOY'S NAME IS.... + ALESSI MEETS HER BROTHER!
author: Lauren & Arie
description:
An emotional day but still one we won't forget. We checked out of the hospital without out baby girl and it was heartbreaking. On positive side Alessi met her baby brother and it couldn't have been cuter :)

SUBSCRIBE to be a part of the fam ❤️

If you haven't seen these videos, check them out... 

Finding out we're having twins! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mr5Ym...
Pregnancy announcement: https://youtu.be/2Up7Jbtg37A 
Meet our babies! Twin birth vlog: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yXXH__JSGrk

Follow us on Instagram too!
https://www.instagram.com/laurenluyendyk
https://www.instagram.com/ariejr
https://www.instagram.com/alessiluyendyk

As always, we love and appreciate every one of you!

-Lauren and Arie Luyendyk

localize.description:
感動的な一日でしたが、忘れられない一日になりました。娘がいないまま退院することになり、胸が張り裂けそうでした。でも、Alessiは弟に会って、これ以上ないほど可愛くなりました。)

サブスクライブして家族の一員になりましょう❤️。
